{{Video:Thread a Needle|}}

== Things You'll Need ==
*a needle
*thread (the same shade as your fabric, or one shade darker)
*scissors

==Tips==
*[[Use a Needle Threader|Consider using a needle threader]]. This device can make the process much easier.<ref>https://www.ifixit.com/Guide/How+to+Use+a+Needle+Threader/21024</ref>

